        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "So we see that if man thinks in a certain way, and eats, drinks, breathes, and sleeps in a corresponding way, he will be well.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
