    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "He does not have to \"treat\" his liver, his kidneys, his stomach, or his heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "There is one Principle of Health in man, which has control over all the involuntary functions of his life; and the thought of perfect health, impressed upon this Principle, will reach each part and organ.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000000_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000000_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Man's liver is not controlled by a liver principle, his stomach by a digestive principle, and so on; the Principle of Health is One.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Imperfect thought causes imperfect functioning, which is disease.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "So the impression became universally disseminated that one who was deprived of food must die in from five to ten days; and numbers of people, when cut off from food by shipwreck, accident, or famine, did die within this period.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Any person, properly educated, can fast from twenty to forty days with little loss in weight, and often with no apparent loss of strength at all.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "The people who starved to death in ten days or less did so because they believed that death was inevitable; an erroneous physiology had given them a wrong thought about themselves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "When a man is deprived of food he will die in from ten to fifty days, according to the way he has been taught; or, in other words, according to the way he thinks about it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000001_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000001_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "So you see that an erroneous physiology can work very mischievous results.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "No Science of Being Well can be founded on current physiology; it is not sufficiently exact in its knowledge.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "With all its pretensions, comparatively little is really known as to the interior workings and processes of the body.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
