        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "These mistaken ideas lead to the thinking of wrong thoughts, and this leads to perverted functioning and disease.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "This, for the most part, is true of all hygiene.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "There are certain fundamental propositions which we should know; and these will be explained in later chapters, but aside from these propositions, ignore physiology and hygiene.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "They tend to fill your mind with thoughts of imperfect conditions, and these thoughts will produce the imperfect conditions in your own body.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "You cannot study any \"science\" which recognizes disease, if you are to think nothing but health.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Then make this conception your guide in thinking of yourself; refuse to entertain for an instant any thought of yourself which is not in harmony with it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000006_000000",
