        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "KNOW that as you think of yourself in unity with this conception, the Original Substance which permeates and fills the tissues of your body is taking form according to the thought; and know that this Intelligent Substance or mind stuff will cause function to be performed in such a way that your body will be rebuilt with perfectly healthy cells.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "The Intelligent Substance, from which all things are made, permeates and penetrates all things; and so it is in and through your body.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "It moves according to its thoughts; and so if you hold only the thoughts of perfectly healthy function, it will cause the movements of perfectly healthy function within you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Hold this thought with perfect faith that it is the fact, the truth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "It is the truth so far as your mental body is concerned.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59779_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59779/6111_59779_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "You have a mind body and a physical body; the mind body takes form just as you think of yourself, and any thought which you hold continuously is made visible by the transformation of the physical body into its image.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "SUPPLEMENTARY INSTRUCTIONS.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "In forming a conception of health, it is necessary to think of the manner in which you would live and work if you were perfectly well and very strong; to imagine yourself doing things in the way of a perfectly well and very strong person, until you have a fairly good conception of what you would be if you were well.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Then take a mental and physical attitude in harmony with this conception; and do not depart from this attitude.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "The scientific way is to sever relations with everything you do not want, and to enter into relations with everything you do want.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Form a conception of perfect health, and relate yourself to this conception in word, act, and attitude.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Guard your speech; make every word harmonize with the conception of perfect health.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "\"I do not feel at all well to day,\" and so on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Say \"I am looking forward to a good night's sleep to night;\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "\"I can see that I progress rapidly,\" and things of similar meaning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "If you follow strictly the way of living prescribed in this book, you will be well; and you certainly CAN follow this way, both in thought and action.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Do not sympathize with people when they complain, or even when they are sick and suffering.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Turn their thoughts into a constructive channel if you can; do all you can for their relief, but do it with the health thought in your mind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Do not let people tell their woes and catalogue their symptoms to you; turn the conversation to some other subject, or excuse yourself and go.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "When we have a few more hundreds of thousands of enlightened thinkers who will not stay where people complain and talk sickness, the world will advance rapidly toward health.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000006_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000006_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "When you let people talk to you of sickness, you assist them to increase and multiply sickness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "What shall I do when I am in pain?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Yes. Do not resist pain; recognize that it is a good thing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Pain is caused by an effort of the Principle of Health to overcome some unnatural condition; this you must know and feel.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Put yourself in full mental harmony with the power which is causing the pain; assist it; help it along.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6111_59791_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6111/59791/6111_59791_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6111",
        "content": "Do not hesitate, when necessary, to use hot fomentations and similar means to further the good work which is going on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
